name: 058 Lisez moi
description:
"It's really important to read the description of things. I called this one "lisez-moi" ("read me"). I wanted to send te idea that rather than just read, the idea is to read between lines. Understand how things works, what is behind a process, a peace of art, a disaster, the lack of socialism in our societies... In this NFT I don't want you to understand the random char, I want you to understand the camera is moving, getting closer the 3D shape. That's the spirit. Lisez moi, getting closer ... (maybe we will see someday that take a step back to see the big picture is very very important too)"
